{"tid":1462442,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"唔係機場既同我收聲","createTime":"2019-08-13T10:35:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T12:38:22.000Z","uid":65748,"like":59,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"804877724120fdbd5c9ec7c18bc4a753098b7fb8","tid":1462442,"uid":65748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:35:14.000Z","msg":"屌你出面個個係到屌阻遊客上機點點點<br />\n根本無遊客屌（除左大陸佬） <br />\n一開始唔夠人個個係T1上上下下咁遊行叫口號 <br />\n對癱瘓一d幫助都無！<br />\n唔係佢地係departures 都撞人根本機管局唔會理鳩你 <br />\n佢地阻左個幾兩個鐘就cancel哂 <br />\n唔係佢地阻人根本唔會取消啊！！！！！<br />\n<br />\n唔該專重係機場手足既決定！<br />\n<br />\n又話不割既？<br />\n<br />\n（發夢去左機場）"},{"pid":"4a88c6889c7bac47292b03d2e13ce1276eed5b64","tid":1462442,"uid":65748,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:35:27.000Z","msg":"721 <br />\n811"},{"pid":"4aec7b6f21ad191eda1c8e9e5d4ce81ca6d2d909","tid":1462442,"uid":65748,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:36:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你出面個個係到屌阻遊客上機點點點<br />\n根本無遊客屌（除左大陸佬） <br />\n一開始唔夠人個個係T1上上下下咁遊行叫口號 <br />\n對癱瘓一d幫助都無！<br />\n唔係佢地係departures 到阻人根本機管局唔會理鳩你 <br />\n佢地阻左個幾兩個鐘就cancel哂 <br />\n唔係佢地阻人根本唔會取消啊！！！！！<br />\n<br />\n唔該專重係機場手足既決定！<br />\n<br />\n又話不割既？<br />\n<br />\n（發夢去左機場）</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n打錯字自膠"},{"pid":"9e43f3473be694361b66e9f7dfe371f48b31648f","tid":1462442,"uid":65748,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:37:21.000Z","msg":"721<br />\n811"},{"pid":"1548902a79cf5f4dd7e764d1a7c4c5dc6fa6bfa6","tid":1462442,"uid":165840,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:37:45.000Z","msg":"人多 自然會 停機<br />\n而唔係 格硬黎<br />\n手足要比d 耐性呀<br />\n借機會 宣傳，而唔係自high<br />\n唔好屌遊客<br />\n唔好阻人走<br />\n唔好逼人做得唔得！<br />\n只會比籍口黑警入黎 依家捉你咋<br />\n依家人少 好危險架<br />\n琴日可以癱瘓到係因為多人令機管局無可避免停飛咋"},{"pid":"671ffebbe663ddc4e2b3d506151413c80993cf68","tid":1462442,"uid":297230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:37:45.000Z","msg":"大家要快d開始傾<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大方向</span></strong></span><br />\n3毛5毛開始想<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">重施故技</span></span></strong>用斟酌「阻人上機」個point黎<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">分化大家</span></span></strong><br />\n但記得大家塞爆機場個<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">目的</span></strong></span>就係要<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">癱瘓機場從而阻人上機</span></span></strong>以造成<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">巨大經濟損失</span></span></strong><br />\n建議集中火力搵出影響力最大嘅時間<br />\n睇下邊段時間最多人能響應，找出平衡<br />\n用隔日形式塞爆<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">以最大化個運動成效</span></span></strong><br />\n隔日嘅好處係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">避免大家過勞和積累</span></strong>過多<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">外國民怨</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>個人認為呢位師兄言之有物<br />\n希望大家可以集思廣益</strong></span><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n[理性討論] 有死線前提搞機場/隔日搞機場比日日搞更好 | LIHKG<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1459515/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1459515/page/1</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地團結一致</span></span><br />\n<br />\nPush"},{"pid":"aaa969bae1ec1a3dacccf31f4c3c034850e9ee90","tid":1462442,"uid":222907,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:38:33.000Z","msg":"仆街啦，關d離港客咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n已經過哂火"},{"pid":"362bd47af7b0e2c0a2bd1911deea8652aef07d61","tid":1462442,"uid":65748,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"1548902a79cf5f4dd7e764d1a7c4c5dc6fa6bfa6","tid":1462442,"uid":165840,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:37:45.000Z","msg":"人多 自然會 停機<br />\n而唔